      <description>&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Professional Summary&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;professional-summary&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#professional-summary&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Results-oriented Software Engineer with a Master&amp;rsquo;s in Computer Engineering and extensive experience at Amazon Web Services (AWS). Proven track record in building cloud infrastructure from scratch, leading technical initiatives for high-scale container services (ECS/Fargate), and pioneering Agentic AI solutions to automate operational workflows.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Technical Skills&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;technical-skills&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#technical-skills&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Languages:&lt;/strong&gt; Java, Python, TypeScript&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cloud &amp;amp; Infrastructure:&lt;/strong&gt; AWS (EC2, ECS, Fargate, Bedrock, Lambda), Docker&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;GenAI / ML:&lt;/strong&gt; Agentic AI, AWS Bedrock, Strands Framework, Claude, Amazon Q&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tools:&lt;/strong&gt; Git, AWS CDK&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Experience&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;experience